## 004_scenario_matching.sql

Purpose:
- store manual match corrections and review decisions

```sql
CREATE TABLE import_review_items (
  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  import_batch_id TEXT NOT NULL,
  raw_payload_json TEXT NOT NULL,
  detected_platform TEXT,
  detected_scenario_name TEXT,
  detected_score REAL,
  detected_occurred_at TEXT,
  reason TEXT NOT NULL,
  status TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  created_at TEXT NOT NULL,
  resolved_at TEXT,
  resolution_json TEXT,
  FOREIGN KEY (import_batch_id) REFERENCES import_batches(id)
);

CREATE TABLE scenario_match_overrides (
  id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
  platform TEXT NOT NULL,
  original_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  normalized_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  benchmark_definition_id TEXT,
  scenario_id TEXT NOT NULL,
  confidence TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'manual',
  created_at TEXT NOT NULL,
  updated_at TEXT NOT NULL,
  UNIQUE(platform, original_name, benchmark_definition_id)
);
```

Rule:
- Manual corrections should be remembered.

