## Transaction Rules

Every import batch must run in a transaction where possible.

If parsing crashes halfway:

```text
batch status = failed
no partial accepted runs unless explicitly committed safely
review items are preserved if created
error message is stored
```

---

## Duplicate Rules

Use a duplicate key like:

```text
platform + scenario name + score + occurred_at + source file hash
```

If no timestamp exists, use:

```text
platform + scenario name + score + import file hash + row index
```

Never silently delete duplicates.

Mark them as skipped or review.

---

## Reanalysis Rules

When benchmark definitions update:

- do not change raw runs
- re-run analysis using new definition
- keep source metadata visible
- show if rank changed because benchmark definition changed

---

## Backup Rules

Before destructive migrations:

- create database backup
- keep at least one previous backup
- show recovery instructions if migration fails

MVP can start with a simple pre-migration copy.
